definition: apart from this/in addition to this
to get rid of/to remove/to exclude/to eliminate/to wipe out/to divide/except/not including

sentences.english: Besides, the McCain dictum is debatable.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，麥凱恩的順口溜也值得商榷。

sentences.english: Despite all this, GE failed to save its top-notch credit rating.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，GE還丟掉了長久以來了最高信用等級。

sentences.english: Furthermore, the rotation of the earth is another factor responsible for earth plate motion.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，自轉的影響也是使板塊運動的力源。

sentences.english: Ms. Yeoman also sells self-illustrated greeting cards.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，雅曼女士還銷售自制的問候卡片。

sentences.english: In addition, with Gio arts Chiellini may not be able to play.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，基耶利尼同吉奧文科也未必能夠出場。

sentences.english: But beyond that his imagination could not travel.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，他的想像力就無從馳騁了。

sentences.english: But amidst all of this, some truths emerge. Leadership and personality matter a lot.
sentences.chinese: 但是除此之外，還要記得領導能力和人格魅力很重要。

sentences.english: And beyond that, swap them for White Jars when you're doing Light Crystal recipes.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，他們掉白水晶瓶子當你做輕食譜。

sentences.english: But beyond this, little of the advice proliferating on the internet is backed by any evidence.
sentences.chinese: 但除此之外，互聯網上盛傳的建議很少有理論依據。

sentences.english: Besides, there is also a balcony next to the living room and one of the bedrooms.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，緊挨起居室和一間臥室有一個陽臺。

sentences.english: Additionally, Confucius placed a strong emphasis on morals and integrity.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，孔子在道德培養方面也具有重要地位。

sentences.english: Mahjong rooms are also available for those who wants to pit their skills against each other.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，我們還擁有多個麻將室供遊客切磋技藝。

sentences.english: In addition to that, I enjoy cooking.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，我也喜歡做飯。

sentences.english: There are one or two hills in Norfolk, but otherwise the landscape is as flat as a pancake.
sentences.chinese: 諾福克有一兩座小山丘，但除此之外是一馬平川。

sentences.english: In addition, you can define the relations between classes.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，你可以定義類之間的關係。

sentences.english: In addition, they also need to provide SGE with EC2 account information.
sentences.chinese: 除此之外，他們還需要提供EC2上的賬戶信息。

definition: apart from/other than/except for/external/outside of/on the other side of/beyond
not only (this one)/not just (...) but also
still/still in progress/still more/yet/even more/in addition/fairly/passably (good)/as early as/even/also/else
